Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:12.86,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人 试着来到 往日的公园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:16.58,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's a feeling never felt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:22.02,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个孩子似的 惧怕着风的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:25.61,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑在回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:34.56,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户之外 是太过宽广的天空 where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:36.65,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:44.64,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这愿望若某天能够实现的话 呐 神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:50.14,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就帮我实现吧 my wish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:56.31,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要听见你的声音 miss you 想要见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.82,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样 都在看着明天吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:06.35,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放跑 timing 不要说得这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:08.70,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:14.80,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最喜欢你 it's too late 从很久以前起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:19.52,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使放弃 也无法回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:24.84,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法 no way 不要简单地下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:28.75,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}只要再 笑一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:35.93,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要互相了解 将真心话互相诉诸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:42.11,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有你的眼泪 也有你的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:49.63,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样的苦痛也不再害怕 两个人话无论哪里都能去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:54.96,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉了我 我不是独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:03.22,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生在世上只为见你 每当我试着轻语这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:08.07,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安便消失不见 心中亮起坚强之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:15.34,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢之意只有你我知晓 随着信号我们共同前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:20.52,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将无法替代的时刻 铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:28.78,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法从这个地方离去 感受着同样的悸动活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:33.48,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一再许诺的约定 想要将其彻底履行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:40.81,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢之意只有你我知晓 随着信号我们共同前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:46.69,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}将无法替代的时刻 铭刻于心

Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 妈妈经常和我说起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Center City里英雄的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三年前 在那座矿山里发生了火灾事故
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多在里面工作的人们 无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正当被火焰包围的人们准备放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受死亡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位矿工说道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不要放弃！”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矿工带领着人们逃到了旧道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为最后希望的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被瓦砾封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对逼近的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位矿工没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位矿工为了拯救人们勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就这么郁闷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能保护好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能像爸爸那样保护好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是爸爸那样的英雄的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞就不会受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来老爸就不是什么英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是保护了Cente rCity大伙的英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种窝囊废才不是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就说说看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄 是什么

Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第22话    回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:06.73,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memories

Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 Heroman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你相遇以来我一直憧憬着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为我懦弱纤小又没胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想变成像爸爸那样雄壮 力气也大 被大家所信赖的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是关于爸爸我几乎没有多少记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被欺负了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爸爸是英雄 所以任何时候都不会哭鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以乔伊也不能轻易哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意啦乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是明天就可以出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这伤是因为我自己不中用才落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护好你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份心意才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才是我们的英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄的话 你最清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩·琼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Center City的英雄是你的…  -布莱恩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人怀念的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在煤矿里工作的人没有不认识他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他儿子乔瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到 你是那个布莱恩和凯瑟琳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是把自己的事情丢一边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴的事情最优先考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此发生了那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常咚咚地敲脑袋这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“这会保护我的”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 他是我们的英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然爸爸是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事…商量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸 果然是英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈给我说的故事 果然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点告诉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然爸爸是英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人怎么说没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐对爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没能好好了解爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说得爸爸这么坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸不是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是个窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你不明事理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸的事 我最清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让你看见我这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哪都别去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很担心哥哥你 不是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止爸爸他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里的同学也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇见乔伊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我对峙的事不可能说得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再和他扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是来道别的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会再见面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈他们就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经讲过别说维鲁的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维鲁已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥才没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 Heroman
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么姐姐要说得爸爸这么坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家都在夸爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找她谈谈吧

Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一发生什么事就来这里传话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.58,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：指乔伊来父母坟前向他们传话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该独立一下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 回答找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说爸不是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有无论如何也原谅不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸他说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸像往常一样出门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六点就回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最后看到的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了好多天 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸再也不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定也忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实老爸说不定是救了很多人性命的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都感谢他 赞扬他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下来的家人要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈把爸爸当作骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像姐姐说得这么坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看过妈妈哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈从不向别人展现眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:15:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论多么伤心 不论多么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 肯定是藏起来哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以不能让我们看见的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独一人地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要老爸还在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们面前逞强 太过逞强…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没多久就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使全世界都赞扬老爸感激老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只想他在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸他装帅 沉浸在奇怪的英雄主义里 最后死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人发笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果给我们家人留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那不怎么干净的头盔而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚咚地敲脑袋这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"这会保护我的"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多

Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:50.61,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澄み渡る空は　知っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:50.61,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万里无云的天空 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:17:01.84,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優しい風なら 知っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:17:01.84,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔和的清风呢 你又知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:07.94,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右左　どちらに進むたとしても同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:07.94,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论左右 往哪走都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:14.24,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私には地図なのない　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:14.24,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有地图 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:19.76,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青空をさす新芽たちのように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:19.76,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像直指青空的嫩芽一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:25.31,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を伸ばしたら　見つけられるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:25.31,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出手的话 应该便能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:30.96,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花咲かせたい　綿毛たちのように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:30.96,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要像胎毛一样 尽情绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:37.75,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨ってるのは　見つけられるわ　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:37.75,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨着 终能寻觅到 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:47.60,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほらよと 日　虹と雲と
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:47.60,插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻声说道你看 是太阳 彩虹和云

Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸有咚咚地敲脑袋的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事在家里一次也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得爸爸比姐姐想象中更为家人着想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会保护我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们 因为有你们 我才能如此努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我莉娜在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里附近全都找遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜她？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 可能不怎么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪 大家都很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是指谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊 为什么知道是这？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电话里听到了浪声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想会不会是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你爸爸吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为爸爸的事和姐姐吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸在我小时候死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我基本没什么爸爸的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 因此我和姐姐感觉比起以前离爸爸更近了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 在这么严重的时候我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以继续努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是Heroman新的能力觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莉娜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有什么事想商量吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再和他扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹顿老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹顿老师问乔伊在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？

Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的heroman讲述的是
